Package com.app.persistence.entity

Class BaseEntity

java.lang.Object
com.app.persistence.entity.BaseEntity
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClientEntity, OrderEntity, ProductEntity, UserEntity, VerificationTokenEntity
@MappedSuperclass public class BaseEntity extends Object
Base class for entities that require an ID field.

This class serves as a common superclass for all entity classes in the application that need an automatically generated unique identifier. It provides the basic functionality for persisting entities in the database with an Id annotated field and a generated value strategy.

The `@MappedSuperclass` annotation indicates that this class is not itself an entity but serves as a base for other entities. It defines common fields and logic for entities in the application.
